{"tid":2115110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地屋企有冇啲咁嘅人？","createTime":"2020-07-19T09:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T10:11:38.000Z","uid":222119,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b95f918349594765178f2401946f53d6eabe1228","tid":2115110,"uid":222119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"依家疫情咁嚴重大家都知啦<br />\n咁我父母係早期買左啲完全冇保證嘅口罩返黎<br />\n點冇保證法？連pm2.5、BFE 、VFE字眼 全部都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地買返黎又從來都冇用過呢啲唔合標準嘅口罩<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>因為佢哋有自己私人嘅口罩</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係KF94 、合格嘅外科口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢講依家屋企啲口罩唔啱規格，防唔到菌 佢地就發曬癲咁屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話如果出事政府會幫我地喎<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁又唔見你地用個啲口罩？</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 究竟佢哋有冇諗過如果我中咗武肺嘅話，佢哋好大機會都會一齊出事？"},{"pid":"23c58b5acbfbadaeefb5fe7b684310b9a389032b","tid":2115110,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"我用銅芯都係咁啦"},{"pid":"8ca0dffe4652e3552125ad1dce83eb26ab01df98","tid":2115110,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"你未出嚟做嘢？"},{"pid":"c740d065e565c080c8427df63eded56589cec54a","tid":2115110,"uid":67041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"你自己唔買？"},{"pid":"0a4d638ddf6085f1b1db2e26704235a2b33021a0","tid":2115110,"uid":222119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ca0dffe4652e3552125ad1dce83eb26ab01df98","tid":2115110,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"你未出嚟做嘢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"依家搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靠之前pt嘅錢唔夠用"},{"pid":"73df9c4e623